programme.title: Scene of the Crime
programme.desc: Scene of the Crime is the title of a mystery anthology series that aired in 1991 and 1992 on CBS, as part of the Crimetime After Primetime late-night block. programme.title: Petticoat Junction

Despite a revolving door of cast changes, the gentle, down-home comedy had a successful seven-year run.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.desc: A widow and her three daughters (and Uncle Joe, who's a-movin' kinda slow) run the Shady Rest Hotel in Hooterville, whose clientele consists mainly of passengers on the spur line of an almost-defunct railroad.
